article_id:1072,category_name:Events,title_name:Story Event Revival, Valentine's Confections, Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2b36a6006082f0ed9a0a249afdc9760c.png,message:<div>The story event revival, Valentine&#39;s Confections, will start <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1581660000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>In the Valentine&#39;s Confections story event, you can use event items acquired by clearing quests from the main campaign and various events to unlock special Valentine&#39;s stories. You&#39;ll be able to check out limited-time stories for the various characters. This time around, you&#39;ll also be able to give your allies Valentine&#39;s presents!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2b36a6006082f0ed9a0a249afdc9760c.png"></div><div>Happy Valentine&#39;s! The season for sharing your feelings with someone important to you is finally here.</div><div><br></div><div>You can defeat fiends to collect items and create special memories with residents of the Halidom, but who will you choose? A strict priestess? A man with love to spare? But there&#39;s no telling who else may make an appearance!</div><div><br></div><div>How much story you experience is up to you... But we hope you enjoy this extra-sweet, gushy time of year, and that you&#39;re looking forward to the Valentine&#39;s Confections story event revival!</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1581573600,update_time1581321378